flowchart TD
    SP[SharePoint Online<br/>System of record]
    ING[Azure Function<br/>Submission discovery]
    SB[Azure Service Bus<br/>Submission queue]
    DW[Durable Workflow<br/>One per submission]
    OUT[SharePoint Results<br/>CSV by form type]

    subgraph WF[Activities inside Durable Workflow]
        EXT[ExtractText]
        CLASS[Classify]
        VAL[ValidateSubmission]
        WRITE[WriteResults]
    end

    YAML[Yaml Definitions<br/>Form types<br/>Attachment types<br/>Rules]
    OCR[Azure Document Intelligence]
    AI[Azure OpenAI / Foundry]
    PY[Deterministic Python Rules]
    ST[Azure Storage<br/>Durable runtime state]

    SP --> ING
    ING --> SB
    SB --> DW
    DW --> EXT
    EXT --> CLASS
    CLASS --> VAL
    VAL --> WRITE
    WRITE --> OUT

    EXT --> OCR
    CLASS --> YAML
    CLASS --> AI
    VAL --> YAML
    VAL --> AI
    VAL --> PY

    DW -. runtime state .-> ST